description:
Guy's Grocery Games - Season 14, Episode 5




Superstars Tournament Part 1

Eight of America's best celebrity chefs are competing against each other in a no-holds-barred $40,000 tournament! First, our Superstars confront every shopper's mortal enemy, the Express Lane! The bottom two chefs must go head-to-head in the single-elimination Redemption Round. In the end, one chef exits while the others stay alive in this five part tournament that will earn one chef big money for charity!




Original Air Date: 20-Aug-2017
